{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Separation of powers and oversight\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Civil liberties and political rights\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Information integrity and media independence\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Institutional accountability\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Use and abuse of emergency powers\
