\f0\b\fs34 \cf2 Updates, Archival Practice, and Use
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
The Democracy Clock is updated regularly, with interim updates issued when major developments materially affect democratic condition. Periodic archival editions preserve immutable snapshots of the record at fixed points in time. Subsequent editions document change rather than overwrite history.\
\
The Democracy Clock may be cited as a standing report. Individual entries may be cited by date and edition. Charts and tables are cleared for reuse with attribution. Analytical disagreement is welcomed.\
